One of items in queue filter settings. There is a combo box that contains options for each filter. They are:
"Ignore (doesn't matter)" in which case the filter is completely ignored - it doesn't matter whether edit matches it or not
"Exclude (must not be)" in this case edit is excluded from queue if it match the filter
"Require" - in this case edit is exluded if it doesn't match the filter
